<div id="c161">
<p>There&#8217;s a perfectly simple and direct test for evil.
If a person is utterly convinced of the correctness of his/her position and refuses to even contemplate that they might perhaps be in error &#8212; if they never step back to question themselves and re-check the belief structures for inconsistency (or become blind to or ignore inconsistencies when pointed out), then they are following the path of evil.</p>

<p>Self-doubt is a necessary condition for Good.</p>

