<p>I agree with this for the most part.  I don&#8217;t think there is any way to label good and evil.  Each and every person has a different view on what is right and wrong.  I think there are people who intentionally do &#8220;bad&#8221; things because they LIKE doing it, but I think there are also people who do bad things because they think it is the right thing to do.  Now, it may or may not be, but that just depends on the person analyzing it.  There&#8217;s no way to label right and wrong, considering there is literally two sides to every argument and action.  Interesting thoughts though; I don&#8217;t understand why people are attacking them so much.</p>

